### Create a new teaching record
POST http://localhost:3000/teach
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

###

### Get all teaching records
GET http://localhost:3000/teach

###

### Get a specific teaching record by user ID and class ID
GET http://localhost:3000/teach/{{userId}}/{{classId}}

###

### Delete a teaching record
DELETE http://localhost:3000/teach/{{userId}}/{{classId}}
